        public Exception getException()
        Gets the optional exception that raised the event, null if unapplicable. If the event is raised due to an error response from the appliance, this field will be of type JCSMPErrorResponseException and the JCSMPErrorResponseException.getSubcode() method can be used to get more information about the error response.
        Returns:
